msgid "## 9 Performance Tuning"
msgstr "## 9 性能调优"

msgid "### 9.1 Recommended Configurations"
msgstr "### 9.1 推荐配置"

msgid ""
"> **Note**: The following configurations are validated in specific test "
"environments and are for reference only. The optimal configuration depends "
"on factors such as maximum input/output length, prefix cache hit rate, "
"precision requirements, and deployment machine ratios. It is recommended to "
"refer to Section 9.2 for tuning based on actual conditions."
msgstr ""
"> **注意**：以下配置在特定测试环境中验证通过，仅供参考。最佳配置取决于最大输入/输出长度、前缀缓存命中率、精度要求和部署机器比例等因素。建议参考第"
" 9.2 节根据实际情况进行调优。"

msgid "#### Table 1: Scenario Overview"
msgstr "#### 表 1：场景概览"

msgid ""
"| Scenario | Deployment Mode | *Total NPUs | Weight Version | Key Considerations |\n"
"|----------|----------------|-------------|----------------|---------------------|\n"
"| High Throughput | Single-Node (TP4, DP4) | 16 (A3) | W8A8 | DP and TP distribute MoE experts across 16 NPUs for maximum throughput |\n"
"| High Throughput | PD Disaggregation (3 nodes) | 48 (3×A3) | W8A8 | 3-node PD separation balances prefill and decode resources for high throughput |\n"
"| Low Latency | Single-Node (TP16) | 16 (A3) | W8A8 | 16-NPU TP minimizes per-token latency with speculative decoding |\n"
"| Long Context | Single-Node (TP8, CP2) | 16 (A3) | W8A8 | 16-NPU TP with Context Parallelism extends context to 135K tokens |"
msgstr ""
"| 场景 | 部署模式 | *NPU 总数 | 权重版本 | 关键考量 |\n"
"|----------|----------------|-------------|----------------|---------------------|\n"
"| 高吞吐 | 单节点 (TP4, DP4) | 16 (A3) | W8A8 | DP 和 TP 将 MoE 专家分布到 16 个 NPU 上以实现最大吞吐量 |\n"
"| 高吞吐 | PD 分离 (3 节点) | 48 (3×A3) | W8A8 | 3 节点 PD 分离平衡 Prefill 和 Decode 资源以实现高吞吐量 |\n"
"| 低延迟 | 单节点 (TP16) | 16 (A3) | W8A8 | 16-NPU TP 通过推测解码最小化每 Token 延迟 |\n"
"| 长上下文 | 单节点 (TP8, CP2) | 16 (A3) | W8A8 | 16-NPU TP 结合上下文并行将上下文扩展到 135K Token |"

msgid ""
"> `*Total NPUs` indicates the total number of NPUs used across all nodes."
msgstr "> `*NPU 总数` 表示所有节点上使用的 NPU 总数。"

msgid "#### Table 2: Detailed Node Configuration"
msgstr "#### 表 2：详细节点配置"

msgid ""
"| Scenario | Configuration | #NPUs | TP | DP | MTP Speculation Num | FUSED_MC2 | EP Switch | Async Scheduling |\n"
"|----------|---------------|-------|----|-------------|--------------------|-----------|-----------|--------------|\n"
"| High Throughput | Single-Node | 16 | 4 | 4 | none | On | On  | On |\n"
"| Low Latency | Single-Node | 16 | 16 | 1 | 3 | Off | On | On |\n"
"| Long Context | Single-Node | 16 | 8 | 1 | none | On | On | Off |"
msgstr ""
"| 场景 | 配置 | #NPU | TP | DP | MTP 推测数 | FUSED_MC2 | EP 开关 | 异步调度 |\n"
"|----------|---------------|-------|----|-------------|--------------------|-----------|-----------|--------------|\n"
"| 高吞吐 | 单节点 | 16 | 4 | 4 | 无 | 开 | 开  | 开 |\n"
"| 低延迟 | 单节点 | 16 | 16 | 1 | 3 | 关 | 开 | 开 |\n"
"| 长上下文 | 单节点 | 16 | 8 | 1 | 无 | 开 | 开 | 关 |"

msgid ""
"> For additional parameter details, please refer to the deployment examples "
"in [Section 5.1](#51-single-node-online-deployment)"
msgstr "> 更多参数详情，请参考[第 5.1 节](#51-single-node-online-deployment)中的部署示例。"

